Name: Snakeez
About the game: SNAKeez is a simple 'snake' classic style game but with different physics.Here you have to collect not apples but eggs and snake's tail grows much faster.As a snake you can move in any direction and turn in any angle,besides,you can't smash your head into the walls.But!It also always moves and needs more eggs.More eggs you eat - more your tail grows.
